node_7.description: This is Maria Lopez's plan for Monday February 13: wake up and complete the morning routine at 6:00 am, spend an hour resting and listening to music from 7:00 am to 8:00 am, head to Hobbs Cafe at 9:00 am, open the Cafe at 10:00 am and work at the counter until 1:00 pm, close the cafe and head home at 1:00 pm, spend the afternoon resting and reading from 2:00 pm to 4:00 pm, do some light activities like knitting from 4:00 pm to 6:00 pm, have dinner at 6:00 pm.
